  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You attempt to calm the target by uttering soothing words in a calm and even tone. The target gains a +1 status bonus to Will saving throws. This bonus increases to +2 against emotion effects.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spell-effects.Item.an4yZ6dyIDOFa1wa]{Spell Effect: Soothing Words}</p>\n<p>In addition, when you Cast this Spell, you can attempt to counteract one emotion effect on the target.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (5th)</strong> The bonus to saves increases to +2, or +3 against emotion effects.</p>"
